# Firebase native config -- not a hard secret (ships inside every built
# APK regardless), but kept out of this public repo's git history as
# defense in depth. Restored in CI from the GOOGLE_SERVICES_JSON_BASE64
# secret; required locally for `flutter build`/`flutter run` on Android
# (get it from Firebase Console > Project Settings > your Android app).
google-services.json
